data.description: Stunning 50 acre property! This home has a large pond & cabin with dock; livestock pen; storage bldgs; and lean-to for equipment or toys. Only 1 owner until the current owners purchased in Nov. 2022 but never moved in due to their military service. The main house has 3 BR & 3 BA, 20’ x 30’ LR has 20’ ceilings with wood beams, full brick wall with a propane-wood burning fireplace, and large 3 season room. Throughout the main areas the walls are California Redwood which is endangered and unharvested today. The primary suite has his & her baths. Upstairs has a loft, 2 BR and Jack & Jill BA. There's a 2 car garage & a paved driveway. The 800+ sq ft cabin is open-living concept with a full kitchen, BA & a huge porch with a private dock leading to the pond stocked with bass. The scenic property's meadows are perfect for hay and are fenced for livestock, a portion of the property is wooded. Included is a well house with a one-horse pump and 15+ sprinkler heads fed by the pond for irrigation.
